    dc:description "Figure 53. Urupelma pampas sp. n. from Peru, Apurimac province, between Ocros and Chincheros, habitus of male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0514012), dorsal view. Scale bar = 10 mm. Photo by R. Kaderka." ;
